                      <p>
                          <i class="fa fa-quote-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                          Dan is a very talented developer who consistently learns new technologies and figures out
                          ingenious ways to use them. In the past few months of working together, in addition to building
                          a production ready IoT capability, he built a VR experience, voice translation services, and many
                          other innovative demos. He is a great catch for any innovative team.
                      </p>
                      <p class="recommender">
                          –France Roy,
                          CTO | AB-InBev (<a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-turcotte-40566817"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square fa-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>)
                      </p>
                  </div>
              </section>
          </div>
